Physics Cheater is a lightweight android app that displays physics formulas for quick reference. Covers electric current, electrostatics, heat, thermodynamics, mechanics (linear and rotational), impulse, momentum, optics, magnetism and work, power and energy. 
Physics Cheater is open source under Apache License 2.0 (more in LICENSE) and is freely available on the Android Market Store at https://market.android.com/details?id=com.ujj.physicscheater.
